Sounds like the fudge hasn't set yet. How long did you have it in the refrigerator? Although I recommend at least two hours, sometimes it takes longer for the fudge to set (depending on the shape and material of your container).<br />
<br />
Once set, the fudge can be cut at cold or room temperatures without a problem.</div>
