					<div class="commentbody"><div class='commentquote'>Eliz wrote:<div class='commentquotebody'>Consequently, I do not use these chips when I don't have to.  I manage and hoard them like gold.  So could I substitute some of the chips in this recipe?  If so, what would I use? A chocolate bar or cocoa?  What components would you tweak in order to accommodate this substitution?<br />
