					<div class="commentbody">I made this for the fist time yesterday, and had leftovers that would not fit in the tin. Decided to try to make some choc mint out of the left overs, 1 tsp of perpermint essence to about 1/3 of the mixture set a little softer than the normal recipe, but tasted GREAT!.<br />
<br />
I'm going to try for bailey's flavour next, with white choc, rum and vanilla. YUM!</div>
